com.myclinic.model

Packages that use com.myclinic.model
Package
Description
com.myclinic.model
The model package contains the class definitions of the domain model classes.
com.myclinic.service
The service package contains the Service-layer class definitions.
com.myclinic.service.dto.readonly
The service.dto.readonly package contains the class definitions of DTO classes used in read-only operations.
com.myclinic.service.dto.update
The service.dto.update package contains the class definitions of the DTO classes used in update operations.
com.myclinic.service.util.mapper
The service.util.mapper package contains DTO-to-Model and Model-to-DTO class mappers.
